1 0 0 1 56 736.0 Tm (than steady.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 722.0 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 56 708.0 Tm (As prey approached, individuals shifted into an intermediate regime of brighter, shorter) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 694.0 Tm (flashes at intervals near nine seconds. The third and most striking regime appeared only in) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 680.0 Tm (the final approach: a brief burst of rapid, high-intensity flickers followed by complete) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 666.0 Tm (darkness for one to three seconds immediately before a strike. We interpret the terminal) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 652.0 Tm (blackout as a means of denying the prey a fixed target at the critical moment.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 638.0 Tm () Tj
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 620.0 Tm (Discussion) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 606.0 Tm (If the light is bacterial, how can the host modulate it so precisely? The escal pore is) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 592.0 Tm (ringed by muscular tissue and pigment shutters, and our timing data are consistent with) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 578.0 Tm (mechanical gating of an otherwise continuous bacterial glow rather than with metabolic) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 564.0 Tm (switching of the bacteria themselves. The host need not turn the light off so much as hide) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 550.0 Tm (it, which is far faster.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 536.0 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 56 522.0 Tm (These findings reframe the anglerfish lure as an instrument played by the fish rather than a) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 508.0 Tm (lamp left burning. They also caution against treating any deep-sea bioluminescence as) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 494.0 Tm (behaviourally inert simply because its biochemical source is symbiotic.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 480.0 Tm () Tj
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 462.0 Tm (Conclusion) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 448.0 Tm (Lure illumination in Melanocetus johnsonii is actively timed and falls into three) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 434.0 Tm (reproducible regimes keyed to prey proximity, including a deliberate pre-strike blackout.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 420.0 Tm (The result argues for renewed attention to the fine temporal structure of deep-sea light) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 406.0 Tm (displays, which low-frame-rate historical surveys would have averaged away into an apparent) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 392.0 Tm (constant glow.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 378.0 Tm () Tj
